room_title: Escape room "Cursed - Egyptian Tomb" by Portsmouth Team Building - Escape Rooms in Portsmouth
room_description: The tomb of the ancient Egyptian King awaits your visit. Hieroglyphs and gods will guide you on the way to uncovering the fate of a lost archaeologist and solving the mysteries of the tomb. You will have 45 minutes to work as a team to return the ancient scarab to the king to rid all the evil spirits.
